{
  "stem": "26486.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then he said-- told us he had sad news to tell us, that we had lost a lot of prisoners.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then we had to get back in the trucks, and getting to Lubeck.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we get to Lubeck, the German people-- but apparently they didn't know what to do to try to make us a little more comfortable.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some had made soup, and some had given-- wanted to give food and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They told us-- the Red Cross said we could accept it, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It had been probably tested.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know, but anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we ate a little bit there, and then, uh, from there, I think they transferred us to trains.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in Lubeck, right near where the buses-- the convoy came.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they put us in sanitary trains with a nurse and a doctor-- the ones that could sit up OK.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Those that were too tired had to lay down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were normally going towards Denmark.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They want to take us to Copenhagen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we got-- I think we were about-- I don't know-- maybe 50 miles away from Lubeck, and they started again shelling.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they stopped the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They made us get down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to hide again in the ditches and, you know, on the side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then we got back on the train, and I think we didn't go too, too far with the train.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They put us back again in buses-- in a bus, I think, like a sanitary bus.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there we went-- that was one night, two nights.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That must have been the third-- that happened in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was at night, then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the next morning then, and we went maybe to noontime.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
